"title": "8612: prayer, and faith",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8612",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Effective prayer depends on faith, especially on a willingness to trust in God's faithfulness to his promises to his people.</p>\n<h2>Faith is necessary in order to approach God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:6\">HEB 11:6</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Faith is necessary to receive benefits from God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:5-Mark6:6\">MRK 6:5–6:6</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:16-Jas5:18\">JAS 5:16–5:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:12\">EPH 3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:22\">HEB 10:22</a></p>\n<h2>Faith is necessary for effective prayer</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:21-Matt21:22\">MAT 21:21–21:22</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:22-Mark11:24\">MRK 11:22–11:24</a><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:5-Jas1:8\">JAS 1:5–1:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:14-Jas5:15\">JAS 5:14–5:15</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ responded to people's need on the basis of faith</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:27-Matt9:30\">MAT 9:27–9:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:5-Matt8:13\">MAT 8:5–8:13</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:1-Luke7:10\">LUK 7:1–7:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:20-Matt9:22\">MAT 9:20–9:22</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:25-Mark5:34\">MRK 5:25–5:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:43-Luke8:48\">LUK 8:43–8:48</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:21-Matt15:28\">MAT 15:21–15:28</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:24-Mark7:30\">MRK 7:24–7:30</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of notable prayers of faith</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:36-1Kgs18:37\">1KI 18:36–18:37</a> <em>Elijah, in contest with the prophets of Baal</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:17-Jas5:18\">JAS 5:17–5:18</a> <em>Elijah, praying about rain</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:19-1Kgs17:22\">1KI 17:19–17:22</a> <em>Elijah and the widow's son</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:32-2Kgs4:35\">2KI 4:32–4:35</a> <em>Elisha and the Shunammite's son</em></p>",
